    Switch Type

    • SMART WIFI LIGHT SWITCH: This smart switch can be controlled using your hand, phone or voice and is also compatible with tAmazon Alexa, Google Assistant, Alarm.com, or Samsung SmartThings. Control your smart light switches remotely with the Deako mobile app.
    • DESIGN: Clean, simple design makes the Deako Smart Switch look great in any home. Flexibility in design lets you customize your home lighting using schedules, timers and scenes.
    • SCHEDULES: Set your lighting to fit your lifestyle. Set times for the smart light switch to turn on and off. For added home security, schedule your outdoor lights to turn on at dusk and off at dawn or your indoor lights to turn on and off while you’re away.
    • TIMERS: Never forget to turn off a light. Add smart light switches to your hallways, bathrooms and bedrooms to ensure the lights or fan go off after a set period.
    • SCENES: Personalize your home lighting to have multiple programmable smart light switches or dimmers work in tandem and turn on or off at once. On your way out the door, press and hold one switch to turn off all your Deako smart devices.
    • EASY INSTALLATION: All Deako light switches install in seconds when you have a Deako backplate with neutral wire connection. You don’t need to hire an electrician, turn off the power or risk electrocution.
    • IDEAL LOCATIONS: The Deako smart light switch works in your outdoor and entryway lights as well as your kitchen, living room, or office. The smart WiFi light switch will upgrade the lighting in any living space.
    • COMPATIBILITY: The Deako Smart Light Switch works on a single pole, 3-way or 4-way circuit. It supports 11A resistive/general use, 1000W incandescent, 600W LED/MLV/ELV, or 1/2 HP loads. A Deako backplate with a neutral wire connection is needed to set up the Deako Smart Switch.

    Product description


    Control remotely

    Seamlessly control your smart light switch with your voice, phone, or hands. Integrates with Amazon Alexa, Google Assistant, Samsung SmartThings, Alarm.com.


    Customize for your lifestyle

    Craft custom lighting schedules to suit your lifestyle and enhance home security. Coordinate multiple smart switches for personalized lighting scenes, and easily power down all devices with a single-switch press for added convenience.


    Bring convenience & security to every room

    Upgrade the lighting in any living space. Install smart light switches for your outdoor and entryway lights, as well as your kitchen, living room, or office.

      Easy setup and installation, MUST HAVE DEAKO SWITCH BOX
      Reviewed in the United States on July 13, 2023
      1) Begin by removing the current switch: -Gently peel off the faceplate from the backplate, exposing the switch. -Locate the blue tab on the switch and pull it towards you to release the switch from the electrical wiring. 2) Insert the new... See more
      1) Begin by removing the current switch:
      -Gently peel off the faceplate from the backplate, exposing the switch.
      -Locate the blue tab on the switch and pull it towards you to release the switch from the electrical
      wiring.

      2) Insert the new smart switch:
      -Take the new smart switch and align it with the opening left by the removed switch.
      -Push the switch into the opening until it fits securely in place.
      -Wait for the green configure button to start flashing:

      3) Once the new switch is inserted, wait for the green configure button on the switch to begin flashing.
      The flashing light indicates that the switch has power.

      4) Pair the switch to the Deco app:
      -Open the Deco app on your smartphone or tablet.
      -Follow the on-screen instructions provided by the app to pair the switch to the app.
      -Note that during the initial setup, you may be prompted to connect to Wi-Fi. Once this is done, it
      won't be necessary for future setups.
